data.description: Settle into Wakefield; an easily accessible quiet family neighborhood near Hwy 90 and Hwy 22; minutes away from downtown Myrtle Beach and even closer to North Myrtle Beach.  This hidden gem sits in the North Myrtle Beach school district.  A large community pool with a Playground and park area is also included in a private cozy corner of this neighborhood.  Large fenced in back yard offers a 10' x 14' patio with options for outdoor activities or a Carolina Room addition.    Newer A/C system both master bath & guest bath upstairs have new "higher" vanity/sinks installed with new light fixtures and newer shower fixtures along with newer toilets in all 3 bathrooms in the home.    Kitchen has new wooden look LVP water/pet proof flooring and new sink fixture.    Carpet throughout house except for tile in front entry, and bathrooms.
